      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户旅程图，场景是\"在电商网站寻找特定商品\"。整体分成两大阶段：进入线上商店，然后是查找具体商品。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Enter online shop",
        "Look for specific product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。第一阶段\"进入线上商店\"里，用户需要先访问网站再登录对吧？登录环节我们之前讨论过要用Etcd集群做会话管理，需要标注出来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit website",
        "Log in",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，登录那里标注一下Infra_EtcdCluster。用户满意度给3分吧，登录体验一般。访问网站给4分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Log in (Infra_EtcdCluster)",
        "Visit website"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一阶段画好了。现在第二阶段\"查找特定商品\"，我梳理一下步骤：先去搜索页、输入关键词、应用筛选条件、浏览结果列表、点进有潜力的商品——这里浏览结果的时候也要标注Redis缓存对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go to search",
        "Search with text input",
        "Apply filter to search results",
        "Scroll through (Infra_RedisCache)",
        "Go to promising product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，搜索结果列表用Redis缓存的。点进商品详情后，用户要阅读描述、查看规格变体、读评价，最后决定是否找到目标商品。这些步骤满意度都标4分，除了\"进入有潜力的商品\"给5分，因为找到心仪商品时用户最满意。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Read product description",
        "Check out product variants",
        "Read reviews",
        "Decide if product found",
        "Go to promising product"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，整个旅程的标题是\"Looking for a specific product\"，需要把Redis缓存也体现在标题里吗？比如括号标注？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title Looking for a specific product (Infra_RedisCache)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，标题加上Infra_RedisCache标注，这样一眼能看出这个旅程主要依赖的缓存基础设施。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title Looking for a specific product (Infra_RedisCache)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。检查一下：两阶段结构清晰，登录和搜索结果浏览都标注了对应的基础设施，九个步骤的满意度评分也按你说的设置了，从访问网站的4分到进入商品页的5分再到决策的4分。",
